creator: RouteThis
descriptionHtml:
Only run this app if you've been referred by a start.ca support agent.

start.ca CARE runs a variety of network tests and diagnostics and allows you to share them with the support representative who's working hard to solve your problem. This information will help them to solve your issue quickly so you can go back to enjoying your Internet package to the fullest! CARE can also allow Start.ca support agents to connect to your modem to run tests and fix settings with your permission.

Note: The Android location permission gives us access to additional network data
descriptionShort: Runs network tests to help start.ca agents solve your network issues
